{"tid":454950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男老師涉強姦醉酒處女教師並於顏射","createTime":"2017-11-01T15:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T13:12:39.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b410537786a214ac923701d64fdcacb1da33ab38","tid":454950,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"27歲男教師2014年9月參加朋友聚會，見初相識的幼稚園女教師於席間飲醉，涉藉詞送對方回家卻帶對方返自己家中強姦，並於對方臉上射精。男教師被控強姦罪，今於高院開審，事主供稱從沒性經驗，知道被告正脫去自己衣物，但當時醉得無力反抗。<br />\n<br />\n洋名Aries的被告鄧庚濤（27歲）今於高院否認於2014年9月27日在一個公共屋邨單位內強姦同齡的X。<br />\n<br />\nX與被告居於同一公共屋邨，案發前兩人並不認識，亦沒有對方的聯絡方法，案法後亦未有再跟對方聯絡，直到2016年X詢問兩人的共同朋友才取得被告聯絡方法。<br />\n<br />\nX稱案發時自己僅能叫「唔好」，感到被告插入時即大叫「好痛」，惟被告卻稱「我都未插入去你就話痛」，之後被告將X強姦，並射精到X臉上。至清晨X上廁後用紙巾抹下體發現有血，加上逐漸酒醒後發現自己被強姦，遂離開被告單位，X指被告的床亦染血。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171101/57404782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F57404782&d=sGH9C0NDuTfP17pJWNnFV26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a232bde5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F57404782&h=00753732\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171101/57404782</a><br />\n<br />\n今次一定不是勞...."},{"pid":"0f0240b319cfb01502209bb21b817eb85784f908","tid":454950,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7eea0357d5c24de951861ae22cf1558c6bb1c238","tid":454950,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:44:34.000Z","msg":"成件事同學校一啲關係都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52009cc43908acbe99d78f552e501c3cdd7e1780","tid":454950,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7148e6b073744bd77ab4f264eb3c2bb5a0923a1f","tid":454950,"uid":83063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2年前發生記憶會衰退  都幾難入罪掛</blockquote><br />\n其實都唔明點解當時唔報警"},{"pid":"0d2b7426154eed6b5eca80c37b858c13e569adb1","tid":454950,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e73ad43a095f3ee2164b5eeb9d4cd02bd0fe142","tid":454950,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2年前發生記憶會衰退  都幾難入罪掛</blockquote><br />\n其實都唔明點解當時唔報警</blockquote><br />\n搵返條友出來先報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相當有趣"},{"pid":"e3549e144428f552e12179730fa135e2ffc47441","tid":454950,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:49:43.000Z","msg":"2年後先告人強姦?<br />\n痴9線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b28bb884eaa74bc2510a673c52d89972b5cd8bb","tid":454950,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:51:21.000Z","msg":"一定係想破處又後悔所以屈人強奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa2f5da6184a1c6773d209e5c6bd0c7bfa4b2f0","tid":454950,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T15:52:02.000Z","msg":"因為公屋，所以罪成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f90f5f31fec83d4b322f3b3df3a0b94785cd40","tid":454950,"uid":129374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T13:12:39.000Z","msg":"哩d案例好撚緊要，唔好以為d港女傾唔掂數就屈鳩人強姦。女事主廿鳩幾歲啦，重係小六女生咩，當時唔報警，兩年後先報，都戇撚鳩鳩。"}]}